For Screaming Vlog 36 we meet up with @salba69, @twistthewrist, @jake_wooten, and @catchsurf Pros @kalanirobb, @johnnyredmond, and @tylerstanaland at Catch Surf HQ in Encinitas, CA! Catch Surf’s @beefs_official gives us a bit of insight on the brand, and explains the similarities between SC and Catch Surf. With stoke searching in mind, we teamed up with Catch Surf to create a series of shred sticks that the crew got to put to the test! After drying off from the water, we go from the waves to the 'crete as the squad heads to Poods Park to catch a session before calling it a day! Hit up our @youtube channel to watch now! Where should we go in the next Screaming Vlog? Let us know in the comments!

node.text:
Turning someone pro starts long before the actual debut of their first pro board. With Henry Gartland, we had been working on this behind the scenes since the start of 2019. As he continued to push his skating, we all got a front row seat to watch him become the pro that we all knew he would be. When Henry left us back in January it was a loss not only to all of us that were close to him, but to the skate community around the world. Although we are still working through this we want you to know that the support and love from everyone out there has been incredible.

It is at the request of the family that we move forward with the release of Henry’s pro boards. The proceeds of which will be donated to The Henry Gartland Foundation. Henry’s father, Eric, explains that the foundation will focus specifically on brain health. We ask that you please visit the website and follow their instagram for updates and to learn more.

The first boards will available around the end of May, which is subject to change. We appreciate your patience and will be releasing 3 decks total for Henry in 2021.

In our hearts forever E Henry Gartland

Please visit TheHenryGartlandFoundation.org for more info.

node.text:
Today we are excited to talk about and put to the test the 7.75 x 31.6 Transcend Dots VX Deck! This board comes equipped with 5 normal plys and 2 layers of our Quad X technology, making these boards super strong. Be sure to stop by your local shop and see if they have this one available. We are also stoked to try out the new @rictawheels Speedrings! Speedrings’ unique core design puts urethane around the bearing bore like a non-cored wheel, giving you the feeling of a traditional wheel with the speed and reduced rolling resistance of a cored wheel. We put Santa Cruz Skateboards Brand Manager @andrewcannon to the test with three different challenges to find out how this setup skates! Hit up our @youtube channel to watch now, and let us know in the comments below what challenges we should throw in the bins next!

node.text:
Finding heavy music through his love for skateboarding, Chase (@hellahammer) fell into addiction at a young age and since getting sober, 9 years ago, has put his time and energy into @gatecreeper and his other creative endeavors. Spend a scorching 120 degree day in the desert with Chase as we talk skateboarding, music, art. Swipe 🆙 in our story to watch now!
🎥: @thekillatapes @ericdanescu
#SantaCruzSkateboards
